A 17-YEAR-OLD youth has been arrested in Motetema, near
Groblersdal, for allegedly murdering his pregnant teen girlfriend on a
Mpumalanga mountain top, police said on Wednesday.It is alleged that the teen beat and assaulted her with
sharp objects on a local mountain after they had an argument about her being
pregnant.Preliminary investigations revealed that the he was
